<div class='media__message'>
<h4 class='h12 talk-link__speaker'>David Bolinsky</h4>
<h4 class='h9 m5'>
<a class='' href='http://www.ted.com/talks/147?language=en' lang='en'>
Visualizing the wonder of a living cell
</a>
</h4>
<div class='meta'>
<span class='meta__item'>
Posted
<span class='meta__val'>
Jul 2007
</span>
</span>
<span class='meta__row'>
Rated
<span class='meta__val'>
Jaw-dropping, Beautiful
</span>
</span>
</div>
